That's what they would say.

00:08:17.997 --> 00:08:19.031
But it's interesting

00:08:19.031 --> 00:08:20.600
what you said about witnessing

00:08:20.600 --> 00:08:22.101
very targeted

00:08:22.101 --> 00:08:23.236
and witnessing something

00:08:23.236 --> 00:08:24.670
that's much less targeted.

